Let y be the liability of a disease on the logit scale, x be a risk factor in standard deviation (SD) units and z be the genotype of a SNP (coded as 0, 1, or 2). The MR estimate of the causal effect of risk factor on disease9 is \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
