We developed an approach called mtCOJO (multi-trait-based conditional and joint analysis; URLs) to perform a GWAS analysis for a trait conditioning on other traits using GWAS summary data (Methods; Supplementary Fig. 5). We then re-ran the GSMR analysis using the adjusted GWAS summary data from the mtCOJO analysis (Methods). The mtCOJO analysis requires the estimates of bxy of the covariate risk factors on the target risk factor and disease, rg among the covariate risk factors, SNP-based heritability (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
